posting_body: ['Call Now -', 'show contact info', 'x 103', 'OR Text', '103', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to text our team.', 'This is a 1 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 858 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Located in the heart of the Dallas-Fort Worth Metroplex, Post Oak Place is situated in Euless, just minutes from Highway 360.', 'This terrific location is convenient to the Dallas/Fort Worth International Airport, the Irving Convention Center, the University of Dallas, Downtown Dallas, and Downtown Fort Worth.', 'Post Oak Place offers newly renovated homes, a swimming pool and heated spa, a fitness studio, and a leash-free dog park!', 'Our apartments feature hardwood-style flooring, walk-in closets, gourmet kitchens with pantries, wood-burning fireplaces, and built-in bookshelves.', 'Features:', 'Hardwood Flooring*, Full-size washer/dryer*, Paint - Upgrade Scheme*, Appliance Premium*, Fireplace*, 2 Inch Blinds*, Designer Lighting*', '*', 'In select units', 'Community Amenities:', 'Leash-Free Dog Park, Outdoor Kitchen, Cyber Cafe, Package Receiving, Covered Parking, Sparkling Swimming Pool, Online Maintenance Requests, Fitness Studio, Lounge Areas, New Convenient Online Payments, Play Park', 'Pet Policy', 'Pet Policy Type: Cat, Dog', 'Max Weight of Pets: 75', 'Pet Policy Fee Max: $388', 'Max Number of Pets: 2', 'Pet Monthly Rent Max: $25', 'Pet Policy: We welcome 2 pets per apartment home.', 'There is a $388 pet fee(non-refundable) per pet.', 'Pet rent is $25 per month, per pet.', 'There is a weight limit of 75 pounds per pet, and aggressive breeds are prohibited.', 'Please call our leasing center for our complete pet policy details.', 'Follow The Link', 'Below:', '<URL>', '53QnV5b2e4']
